text: Mama, May I go to Sarah Walker's right from school today?
Promise I'll be home in time for dinner. Mom, what do you say?
I'd like to say yes...But your room's a mess!
No! Next time clean your room before you ask me
Mama, may we go out to the playground,it's a sunny day
Swing on swings and hang out in the sandbox. Mom, is that ok?
You can't go. Not all alone
No! Tell you what, I'll take you to the playground Make sure that you are safe
Mama, May I have some ice cream? Can I buy this Game?
Mama, May I Get a puppy? Can I stay up late?
Mama, may we go to Jackie's party? Six o'clock tonight.
We have cleaned our rooms and done our homework, Mom, Is that alright?
